Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是为了促使改革者出现而被人为制造出来的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是改良者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把吠陀还给我们  李本兹·阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果改良者进化了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经成为了超越改良者  成为真正的改革者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一枪我不会故意打偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？  为什么你会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放下武器投降吧  我不会为难你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比利  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白么？  是为了实现永久的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而实现这一目标最大的障碍就是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说要接受改革者的支配么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:04:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被更优秀的存在所统帅  理论上这也是正确的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且为了引导人类而被创造出来的他们  也不会向我们索求什么回报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是很理想的关系么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话就会失去自由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全的自由便是对道德的放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其结果只有毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在有序的社会结构里  人们都满足于有限的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遵守既定的规则也会比较安心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「实现根除战争」  究其本质  其实是你们在扰乱世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不明白  现在把世界交给改革者才是与真正根除战争维系在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有史以来人们梦寐以求的理想乡即将实现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是由我们自己构筑的未来根本没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:05:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不由自己纠正过去犯下的错误的话  真正的未来是不会到来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真顽强啊  Celestial什么什么的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,混账家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GN-Archer被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,粒子残量已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身体也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙慈  沙慈·克洛斯罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,带上她到安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该说过的  我是超越了改革者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会把吠陀交给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  将要引导人类的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Celestial Being…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和妈妈的仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧  死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易…丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙…慈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝  你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是成为纯种的改革者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少得意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希琳  使用TRANS-AM Attack
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了？  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路…路易丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以自己的意识构筑未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你…就不能明白呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,皇…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿里路亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死  到此为止了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话托勒密会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行  不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,米蕾娜  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,导弹剩得不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊恩  琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的生命…正在消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,混账家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事…怎能让它发生啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什  什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种GN粒子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这光  不是战斗产生的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那光芒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这光一定是刹那战斗的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生命的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:10:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,改变吧  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代替没能将这一切改变的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  为了创造未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要改变——！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脑…脑量子波被扰乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是那台Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有那台Gundam存在的话  就算是我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可不仅仅是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,李杰尼·雷杰塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成为纯种的改革者的脑量子波与Twin-Drive联动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,纯度增加的GN粒子能扩张人的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达成完全的进化了么  刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是真正的改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？  这种不舒服的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你这样的家伙把哥哥他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子是那家伙的弟弟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宰了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老子就是老子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,灭了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别分心  阿里路亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈里路亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看好玛丽就行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么  这种不可思议的现象？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脑中居然有声音直接响起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  比利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明知道你的心意  却还向你撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…不要  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…为了实现永久的和平…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了这个才决定要战斗的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…  一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…明明一直爱着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…安德烈少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又有声音  是佩丽丝中尉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.68,0:13:48.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  即便继续对你心存怨恨  最终找你报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校也一定不会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住口！  你这个叛徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么把亲生父亲…  把上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人背叛了军队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遭报应也是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他所做的是破坏永久的和平的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校不是会做那种事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  那家伙是能对母亲见死不救的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能相信么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不能相互理解呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…  那个人什么都没有说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有借口  没有谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不了解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才杀了他  亲手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要上校理解你的话  为什么不去理解上校呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校也一定在为你着想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么那时候什么也没对我说？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不和我说的话  不是什么都不明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不和我说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌机已击坠80%
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能松懈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了？  身上的疼痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙慈  沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙慈  我再也不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不用说  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  这种温暖的光是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉心都快融化了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是他心中的光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,照亮未来的光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吠陀的位置在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红哈罗  机体拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的GN粒子是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把我的脑量子波扰乱了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等待这个时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,李杰尼·雷杰塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的连接被吠陀拒绝了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你将系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,李本兹  我不会让你为所欲为的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  特瑞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  Se…Seraphim启动了审判领域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(484,356)\fs22}Trial Field
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.04,0:17:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与吠陀连接的机体相继停下来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吠陀的辅助断开了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的特瑞亚·埃德！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回吠陀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来  战斗就能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于用上那个了啊  特瑞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特瑞亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧  玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事…  已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  阿里路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到  到底怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！ 给我动起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没资格责怪哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么也不能放过这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等着！你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你无路可逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…  就是这家伙将爸爸  妈妈还有艾米都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莱尔  我们俩曾经心意相通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经心意相通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亚琉  多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能明白人与人可以相互理解的世界并不是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  就算被世界疏远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使身负罪责
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为Celestial Being的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是吠陀的本体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…特瑞亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特瑞亚·埃德！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,此仇必报！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么擅自就认为我已经死了可真是伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里  你在哪里？特瑞亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我的意识已完全与吠陀相连
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吠陀？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很庆幸自己是改革者…  不  是改良者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这能力能够拯救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我通过与吠陀相连  从而得知了所有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就告诉你  伊奥利亚计划的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托勒密  我暂时回来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.73,0:22:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奥利亚计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的武力介入行动尽管自我矛盾  却促成了世界的统合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我们自身终会灭亡  也能使人类的意志得以统一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.40,0:22:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了防止人类在心怀斗争的情况下  向外太空进发
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人类只有改变  才能创造出未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了做好准备  与迟早会邂逅的异种进行对话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.14,0:23:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了这些  我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…必须要相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.01,0:23:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特瑞亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Seraphim  严重受损！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.08,0:23:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特瑞亚呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有反应…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.37,0:23:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再好好找一找！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在审判领域中  还有能动的敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了改革者的改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,李本兹·阿尔马克！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该感谢我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.70,0:23:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你之所以能得到这能力  都是因为我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.88,0:23:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.01,0:24:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,李本兹·阿尔马克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.59,0:24:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.41,0:24:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,达成变革的二人赌上未来  投身最后一战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.40,0:24:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  「再生」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.19,0:24:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新时代的帷幕拉开了
